OL,5, A union has warned P&O Ferries it faces
OL,6, a "summer of disruption" when it       
OL,7, resumes passenger services from        
OL,8, Scotland to Northern Ireland this week.
OL,10,FThe RMT union said it will target ports
OL,11,Fwhen the ferry operator starts running 
OL,12,Fits "ships of shame" again.            
OL,14,FP&O sparked outrage when it sacked 800 
OL,15,Fstaff last month with a plan to replace
OL,16,Fthem with cheaper agency workers.      
OL,18,FPassenger services from Cairnryan to   
OL,19,FLarne have been suspended since, but   
OL,20,Fare now due to resume on Thursday.     
